    "Table 4 summarizes the results of our mediation analysis.",
    "Both paths (a × b [β = 0.259] and c [β = 0.816]) are significant.",
    "The proportion of the total effect on HR-related AI implementation ability mediated by AI orientation is 0.241.",
    "Hence, we conclude support for H4.",
    "Hypotheses H5a and H5b propose moderation effects of firm type on the effects of TMT AI literacy on AI orientation (H5a) and HR-related AI implementation ability (H5b)."
